---
// src/pages/refund.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="Refund Policy — ATEC Gurdaspur" noIndex={true}>
<style>
  .policy-hero { background:#0f2a5c; padding:56px 32px 44px; text-align:center; color:#fff; }
  .policy-hero h1 { font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:2rem; font-weight:900; margin:0 0 8px; }
  .policy-hero p { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size:14px; }
  .policy-body { max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 32px 80px; }
  .policy-body h2 { font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.2rem; font-weight:800; color:#0f2a5c; margin:32px 0 10px; }
  .policy-body p,.policy-body li { font-size:15px; color:#475569; line-height:1.8; margin:0 0 12px; }
  .policy-body ul { padding-left:20px; }
  .policy-body a { color:#0f2a5c; }
  .last-updated { background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:8px; padding:12px 16px; font-size:13px; color:#94a3b8; margin-bottom:32px; }
  .highlight { background:#fefce8; border:1px solid #fde047; border-radius:10px; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .highlight strong { color:#713f12; }
</style>
<div class="policy-hero">
  <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
  <p>Our commitment to a fair and transparent refund process</p>
</div>
<div class="policy-body">
  <div class="last-updated">Last updated: June 2026</div>

  <div class="highlight">
    <strong>Quick summary:</strong> Full refund within 3 days of payment if you haven't accessed more than 2 lessons. After 3 days or 2 lessons, no refund — but you may transfer to another batch.
  </div>

  <h2>1. Online Courses</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Within 3 days of payment, 0 or 1 lessons accessed:</strong> 100% refund, no questions asked.</li>
    <li><strong>Within 3 days of payment, 2+ lessons accessed:</strong> No refund. Course transfer available.</li>
    <li><strong>After 3 days:</strong> No refund. You may transfer to a different batch of the same course within 6 months.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Hybrid / Classroom Courses</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Before batch start date:</strong> 100% refund if cancelled at least 48 hours before.</li>
    <li><strong>On or after batch start date:</strong> No refund. Transfer to next batch available.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How to Request a Refund</h2>
  <p>Email <a href="mailto:atecgsp@gmail.com">atecgsp@gmail.com</a> with subject line "Refund Request — [Your Name] — [Course Name]" within the eligible window. Include your enrolment details.</p>
  <p>Refunds are processed within 7–10 business days to the original payment method.</p>

  <h2>4. Non-Refundable Items</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Registration or processing fees (if applicable)</li>
    <li>Physical materials or kits already dispatched</li>
    <li>Courses accessed beyond the refund window</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about a refund? Call <a href="tel:+917009933289">+91 7009933289</a> or email <a href="mailto:atecgsp@gmail.com">atecgsp@gmail.com</a>.</p>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
